snippet.title: Breaking News-Gal gadot join ben affleck & amber heard on the red carpet the Justice Coalition
snippet.description:
Breaking News-Gal gadot join ben affleck & amber heard on the red carpet the Justice Coalition
GAL Gadot led the troops and stood out from the crowd as she dazzled with her fellow stars at the world premiere of Justice League last night. The Wonder Woman star has reprised her role for the latest edition to the DC Extended Universe, and looked incredible in a silver and gold dress with a thigh high slit. Gal looked delighted to be at the event as she joined her pals for a photocall Looking every inch Amazonian warrior princess, Gal made a lasting impression in the metallic outfit – especially as she stood alongside her allmale League mates. Ben Affleck looked dapper in a suit and healthier than after completing a stint in rehab for alcohol addiction. Preparing to don the iconic mask again as the Caped Crusader, Ben looked in much better spirits as he laughed and joked with his costars during a photocall that saw the entire team unite in their finest.
